Stay Safe Online – Prevention Checklist

1. Never share your UPI PIN or OTP with anyone
2. Do not scan QR codes to receive money
3. Verify unknown calls or messages before taking action
4. Use strong and unique passwords
5. Enable two-factor authentication on apps
6. Avoid clicking on suspicious links
7. Use only official and trusted payment apps
8. Regularly check your bank statements
9. Do not share personal or financial information online
10. Immediately report fraud to the National Cyber Crime Portal (cybercrime.gov.in)
11. Call Helpline Number: 1930 in case of financial fraud
